WARNING:  emaj_drop_extension: There are remaining roles (_regress_emaj_adm1, _regress_emaj_adm2) who have been granted emaj_adm role.
WARNING:  emaj_drop_extension: For these reasons, emaj_adm has not been dropped by this script.
